FleetCor Technologies, Inc. Key Developments

FleetCor Technologies, Inc. to Report Q2, 2017 Results on Aug 03, 2017
Jul 20 17
FleetCor Technologies, Inc. announced that they will report Q2, 2017 results at 5:00 PM, Eastern Standard Time on Aug 03, 2017


FleetCor Technologies, Inc., Q2 2017 Earnings Call, Aug 03, 2017
Jul 20 17
FleetCor Technologies, Inc., Q2 2017 Earnings Call, Aug 03, 2017


the Klein Law Firm Files Class Action Lawsuit against FleetCor Technologies, Inc
Jul 17 17
The Klein Law Firm announces that a class action complaint has been filed on behalf of shareholders of FleetCor Technologies, Inc. who purchased shares between February 5, 2016 and May 2, 2017. The action, which was filed in the United States District Court for the District of Georgia, alleges that the company violated federal securities laws. The complaint alleges that throughout the class period, defendants made materially false and/or misleading statements and/or failed to disclose that the company misled investors regarding the sources of and reasons for its earnings and growth and the company falsely stated that it clearly discloses its fees to customers and that its business is focused on helping employers control spending and save money.


