Key Highlights
FleetCor Technologies, Inc. (FT) focuses on offering fuel cards and workforce payment products. The company along with its subsidiaries offers a range of cards, commercial payment solutions and data management solutions. Its product portfolio includes fuel cards, cash cards, fleet cards and food vouchers.  Its service offering includes payment solutions, payment processing and information management, outsourcing services, mobile telemetric services, fleet maintenance management services and employee benefit and transport related payments services. The company offers its products and services to oil companies, petroleum marketers, government entities, businesses, retailers and commercial fleets. The company distributes its products and services through direct and indirect channels which include value-added resellers (VARs) and other referral partners. The company operates in North America, Latin America, Europe, Australia and New Zealand. FT is headquartered at Norcross, Georgia, the US.

